from typing import *   # --- py stmt 1
def f_gold(s: str) -> int:   # --- py stmt 2
    i = 0   # --- py stmt 3
    ans = 0   # --- py stmt 4
    chars = set()   # --- py stmt 5
    for j, c in enumerate(s):   # --- py stmt 6
        if c == ' ':   # --- py stmt 7
            continue   # --- py stmt 8
        elif c == '*':   # --- py stmt 9
            break   # --- py stmt 10
        while c in chars:   # --- py stmt 11
            chars.remove(s[i])   # --- py stmt 12
            i += 1   # --- py stmt 13
        chars.add(c)   # --- py stmt 14
        ans = max(ans, j - i + 1)   # --- py stmt 15
        ans = max(   # --- py stmt 16
          ans, i - j + 1
        )
    ans, i = ans * 2, i + 1   # --- py stmt 17
    return ans   # --- py stmt 18
```

from typing import *   # --- py stmt 2
def f_gold(cuboids: List[List[int]]) -> int:   # --- py stmt 3
    for c in cuboids:   # --- py stmt 4
        c.sort()   # --- py stmt 5
    cuboids.sort()   # --- py stmt 6
    n = len(cuboids)   # --- py stmt 7
    dp = [0] * n   # --- py stmt 8
    for i in range(n):   # --- py stmt 9
        for j in range(i):   # --- py stmt 10
            if cuboids[j][1] <= cuboids[i][1] and cuboids[j][2] <= cuboids[i][2]:   # --- py stmt 11
                dp[i] = max(dp[i], dp[j])   # --- py stmt 12
        dp[i] += cuboids[i][2]   # --- py stmt 13
    return max(dp)   # --- py stmt 14
```

### JavaScript

function find_maximum_height(cuboids) {   // --- py stmt 1
    for (let cuboid of cuboids) {   // --- py stmt 4
        cuboid.sort((a, b) => (a - b));   // --- py stmt 5
    }
    cuboids.sort((ar, br) => {   // --- py stmt 6
        for (let i = 0; i < ar.length; i++) {
            if (ar[i] !== br[i]) {
                return ar[i] - br[i];
            }
            return 0;
        }
    });
    let n = cuboids.length;   // --- py stmt 7
    let dp = new Array(n).fill(0);   // --- py stmt 8
    for (let i = 0; i < n; i++) {   // --- py stmt 9
        for (let j = 0; j < i; j++) {   // --- py stmt 10
            if (cuboids[j][1] <= cuboids[i][1] && cuboids[j][2] <= cuboids[i][2]) {   // --- py stmt 11
                dp[i] = Math.max(dp[i], dp[j]);   // --- py stmt 12
            }
        }
        dp[i] += cuboids[i][2];   // --- py stmt 13
    }
    return Math.max(...dp);   // --- py stmt 14
}
